{"tid":1381411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"試談通訊策略","createTime":"2019-07-29T08:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T05:16:22.000Z","uid":267702,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e254ffec788674d84ea7157705253a918e792ed1","tid":1381411,"uid":267702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:33:15.000Z","msg":"隨住近日既夢遊愈演愈烈，元朗 + 港島西兩役，幾十個勇士被捉 ... 再咁落去，前線既人只會愈黎愈少！！<br />\n<br />\n大家都好清楚問題出於各線路既<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 協調</span></span></strong> 出左問題！！ <br />\n<br />\n向冇大台，冇人可以話事既情況下，我會將示威者分為 3 類：<br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: maroon;\">前線勇武部隊</span><br />\n2. <span style=\"color: teal;\">中間遊走半勇武部隊</span> <br />\n3. <span style=\"color: navy;\">後勤部隊</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">申利 ： 我係向前線遊走既 FA</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">前線勇武部隊：不知進退 </span></span><br />\n呢個問題，其實存在一定程度上既誤會。前線唔退，往往係因為位置<span style=\"color: red;\">敏感</span>，以及不清楚其他線路情況，怕後撤會為其他線路帶黎災難。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中間遊走半勇武部隊 ： 無牌軍師</span></span><br />\n由於可以遊走，以致佢地對附近各線路既情況，<span style=\"color: red;\">相對</span>較其他位置既人清楚，於是大家會不斷發出各類消息，訊息非常混亂。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">後勤部隊 ： 忠實既支持者</span></span><br />\n佢地裝備極簡，易受攻擊，係最需要保護既一群；雖然係咁，佢地卻係最多人既一群， 佢地盡可能為前線提供一切需要既野，任勞任怨。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">前線唔退，我地後邊係唔會走；後邊唔走，我地前面點可以退。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢個講法，我個人最早係向沙田夢遊果陣聽到。其後，愈聽愈多，證明係我地依嫁出黎夢遊既最大問題。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 入正題 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n個人認為，我地應該發展一套簡單既指令系統。<br />\n例如 ： 建立一群為數<span style=\"color: red;\"> 10-20</span>人既旗手，佢地係<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立</span>於任何人，佢地既唯一作用係<span style=\"color: red;\">傳達</span> <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">各大群組 </span></span> 或 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">各條戰線</span></span> 既訊息。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>原因 I ：</strong></span></span><br />\n最原始既旗手系統可以令所有指令，以<span style=\"color: red;\">迅速</span>不受<span style=\"color: red;\">干擾</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">直接簡單</span>及不帶任何其他情感上既表達，而去作出有效傳達。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>原因 II ：</strong></span></span><br />\n其他群組既人可以<span style=\"color: red;\">專注</span>做自己要做既野；旗手<span style=\"color: red;\">高舉並搖動</span>旗幟果陣，就算戰線被狗分割，做駁腳既旗手都可以見到，繼而作出訊息傳遞。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>原因 III ：</strong></span></span><br />\n旗手只<span style=\"color: red;\">反映</span> + <span style=\"color: red;\">傳達</span>訊息，任何人可以根據自己當刻見到既旗幟顏色而去作出個人既決定，絕對係 ： 兄弟爬山、人各有各做、無大台。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做法舉例 ：</span></span><br />\n每條戰線，應該有一個旗手，戰線同戰線之間既轉角，都有旗手作駁腳。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前線 A : </span><br />\n因爲狗既最新行動，而作出決定，例如 - <span style=\"color: red;\">撤</span>！ 於是，旗手高舉並搖動旗幟，做駁腳既旗手馬上做出相應動作。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前線 B : </span><br />\n因為<span style=\"color: red;\">前線 A</span> 作出了後撤既指令，前線 B 就可決定最新應對方法，然後作出回應。例如，<span style=\"color: red;\">守或撤</span>。於是，旗手高舉並搖動旗幟，做駁腳既旗手馬上做出相應動作。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中間遊走半勇武部隊及後勤部隊 :</span><br />\n作出相應對策。例如，物資轉移。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">* 顏色既選擇 + 配搭 + 背後意義，可以由旗手隊議定。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">小弟第一次寫長文，本住幫手解決問態既心態，請唔好插咁大力 ... 大家多多指教，齊心就事成！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">不分化 &bull; 不割席 &bull; 不篤灰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"dbc509b91b71800a015f18aef4ac0e7540f76c9d","tid":1381411,"uid":263161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:34:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d1bf380c6c9690293e4c2d52b2aedd9549ca9f3","tid":1381411,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:35:31.000Z","msg":"其實已經開始試行<br />\n<br />\n［置頂 728上環見］香港首次旗手小隊上線啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1374922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1374922</a>"},{"pid":"3198faa29886fafa9311a70b055d1492e521e200","tid":1381411,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:50:36.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a89ccc781b929c9a2326f0e0d87dcfd1590bb33a","tid":1381411,"uid":267702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3d1bf380c6c9690293e4c2d52b2aedd9549ca9f3","tid":1381411,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:35:31.000Z","msg":"其實已經開始試行<br />\n<br />\n［置頂 728上環見］香港首次旗手小隊上線啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1374922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1374922</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:54:11.000Z","msg":"我希望旗幟係簡單鮮明，易容制作。"},{"pid":"52e252304532e5f21d041a3c7de3f0bf51687180","tid":1381411,"uid":267702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:05:01.000Z","msg":"自推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3152a381c5a8fa041fd72a8643ce5a19bbd72e25","tid":1381411,"uid":267702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:10:14.000Z","msg":"再自推"},{"pid":"9168f3cf894f21b94014f0160131fc4edc7dcbfe","tid":1381411,"uid":275091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:29:01.000Z","msg":"非常贊成須加強溝通。<br />\n巴打要考慮埋：<br />\n舉旗先後<br />\n狗都會睇到既問題"},{"pid":"d23db976977b1cfc6d0fc921735e5035be2cd7c5","tid":1381411,"uid":267702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9168f3cf894f21b94014f0160131fc4edc7dcbfe","tid":1381411,"uid":275091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:29:01.000Z","msg":"非常贊成須加強溝通。<br />\n巴打要考慮埋：<br />\n舉旗先後<br />\n狗都會睇到既問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:03:14.000Z","msg":"其實預左佢知，但重點係我地唔會亂。<br />\n我地人多，只要行動一致，唔亂，就算佢地知都吹我地唔脹！"},{"pid":"0bee13422d8393d5baafee5866dc127ad1449a93","tid":1381411,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:03:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81d2548dc516e7e5a583374ee7f5e3f32994dd2a","tid":1381411,"uid":112433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:04:58.000Z","msg":"推 引討論"},{"pid":"d2220462760063f5c726950e6eac0ed4aa74130f","tid":1381411,"uid":275091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:27:57.000Z","msg":"推 光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"a43571263f21066b72b48bbce20952f15020fa31","tid":1381411,"uid":267702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:16:22.000Z","msg":"再推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}